title: Cancerslug - Live Video Bootlegs
description:
Cancerslug are a band from Huntsville, Alabama, prominent in the Horror Punk and Gothic/Death Rock scenes. The band has gone through many line-up changes since its inception in 1996, with frontman Alex Story being the only consistent member. Bitrate and codecs vary, as these are bootleg recordings.
